1. *Nečemu* se nadam da će se sve dobro završiti. (I'm hoping something will end well.)
2. Nisam baš zadovoljan *nečemu* što je on rekao. (I'm not really pleased with something he said.)
3. On se nada da će uspeti da se izbori sa *nečemu* što ga muči. (He hopes he will be able to fight something that bothers him.)
4. Svi smo se čudili *nečemu* što se dogodilo. (We were all surprised by something that happened.)
5. Nismo znali zašto se on tako ponašao prema *nečemu*. (We didn't know why he was behaving like that towards something.)